 @dev This contract manages a decentralized crowdfunding platform using Ethereum blockchain. It allows users to create, fund, and manage crowdfunding projects with smart contracts to ensure transparency and security.

devdoc.details: This contract manages a decentralized crowdfunding platform using Ethereum blockchain. It allows users to create, fund, and manage crowdfunding projects with smart contracts to ensure transparency and security.

contribute(uint256).details: Allows users to contribute to a project. Contributions can only be made if the project is open and not yet expired.

params.projectId: The ID of the project to contribute to.

createProject(string,string,uint256,uint.details: Creates a new project with the specified details. Only callable by registered users.

params.duration: Duration in seconds for which the project will accept contributions.
params.goal: The funding goal to be reached.
params.name: Name of the new project.

refund(uint256).details: Issues refunds to contributors if the project does not meet its funding goal by the deadline. Can be called by contributors.

params.projectId: The ID of the project from which to claim a refund.

releaseFunds(uint256).details: Releases funds to the project owner if the funding goal is met. Can only be called by the project owner or contract admin.

params.projectId: The ID of the project for which funds are to be released.
